OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FHe started out in newspapers in the
OL,7,F1960s, working for the Daily Express -
OL,8,Feven reporting from the Vietnam War.
OL,10,FBut his love of football was always
OL,11,Fthere: he played while at Oxford
OL,12,Fbefore going on to play for the
OL,13,Ffamously amateur Corinthian Casuals.
OL,15,FHe later played for Altrincham in the
OL,16,Fthen Cheshire League.
