OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FThe BBC ran a contest to find a new
OL,7,Fcommentator to head to Mexico for the
OL,8,F1970 World Cup.
OL,10,FHarrison came third, losing out to
OL,11,FLiverpool and Scotland striker Ian St
OL,12,FJohn and eventual winner Idwal Robling.
OL,14,FThe competition was judged by a panel
OL,15,Fwhich included Sir Alf Ramsey and
OL,16,FSports Minister Denis Howell.
OL,18,FBut the Beeb's loss was ITV's gain.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/12
