OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FSomeone at ITV Sport must have been
OL,7,Fwatching, and Harrison soon found
OL,8,Fhimself working for channel 3,
OL,9,Fcovering the Mexico 70 World Cup.
OL,11,FHe covered Group Two in Puebla and
OL,12,FToluca, which featured eventual
OL,13,Ffinalists Italy along with Uruguay,
OL,14,FSweden and Israel. He went on to cover
OL,15,Fsix World Cup tournaments over the
OL,16,Fcourse of his career.
