OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FHe was the commentator on any game
OL,7,Fbroadcast from the Anglia region; as
OL,8,FBrian Moore used to say: "The pictures
OL,9,Fcome from Anglia, the commentator is
OL,10,FGerry Harrison."
OL,12,FHe later went on to become Anglia's
OL,13,Fhead of sport, where he worked
OL,14,Falongside Stuart Jarrold, who
OL,15,Fremembers his former colleague fondly.
OL,17,F"He was the voice of East Anglian
OL,18,Ffootball for years and he was a
OL,19,Fconsummate professional," he said. "A
OL,20,Ffantastic chap to work with and a
OL,21,Fthoroughly decent bloke.
