OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,F"He got on well with everybody. I
OL,7,Fnever, in nearly 10 years of working
OL,8,Fwith him, ever had cross word.
OL,10,F"He was so diligent in his preparation
OL,11,Fthat he made commentating sound easy.
OL,12,FIt isn't, but he did all his research
OL,13,Fand he was a thoroughly lovely, lovely
OL,14,Fchap."
OL,16,FHarrison left Anglia in the early
OL,17,F1990s, going on to work with
OL,18,Finternational broadcasters and even
OL,19,Fworked on an early version of FIFA's
OL,20,FClub World Cup.
