OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FHe helped production company IMG start
OL,7,Fits involvement in football, which
OL,8,Feventually helped shape the way the
OL,9,FPremier League was covered. He was
OL,10,Falso a consultant for FIFA Films.
OL,12,FHis death also drew tributes from
OL,13,Ffellow commentators.
OL,15,FIan Darke, who now works for ESPN,
OL,16,Fsaid he was a pleasure to work with
OL,17,Fand a big loss.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G9/12
