OL,3,CTributes to broadcasting legend Gerry
OL,4,CHarrison
OL,6,FAnother ex- ITV News Anglia sports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent was Tony Jones, who
OL,8,Fdescribed Harrison as more than just a
OL,9,Fsports reporter.
OL,11,F"He gave me my first job in television
OL,12,Fback in 1982 with Anglia," remembered
OL,13,FJones, "and I don't think I'm alone in
OL,14,Fsaying he was an inspirational figure
OL,15,Fbecause I spoke to so many producers
OL,16,Fand directors and people within the TV
OL,17,Fbusiness who said that they've learnt
OL,18,Fso much from him.
OL,20,F"He always set the highest possible
OL,21,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                   G10/12
